038   /** Default value */
039   public static final SubItems DEFAULT = create().build();
040
041   /**
042    * Instantiates a new builder for this class.
043    *
044    * @return A new builder object.
045    */
046   public static Builder create() {
047      return new Builder();
048   }
049
050   /**
051    * Returns <jk>true</jk> if the specified annotation contains all default values.
052    *
053    * @param a The annotation to check.
054    * @return <jk>true</jk> if the specified annotation contains all default values.
055    */
056   public static boolean empty(org.apache.juneau.annotation.SubItems a) {
057      return a == null || DEFAULT.equals(a);
058   }
059
060   /**
061    * Merges the contents of the specified annotation into the specified generic map.
062    *
063    * @param om The map to copy the contents to.
064    * @param a The annotation to apply.
065    * @return The same map with the annotation contents applied.
066    * @throws ParseException Invalid JSON found in value.
067    */
068   public static JsonMap merge(JsonMap om, SubItems a) throws ParseException {
069      if (SubItemsAnnotation.empty(a))
070         return om;
071      Predicate<String> ne = StringUtils::isNotEmpty;
072      Predicate<Collection<?>> nec = CollectionUtils::isNotEmpty;
073      Predicate<Map<?,?>> nem = CollectionUtils::isNotEmpty;
074      Predicate<Boolean> nf = ObjectUtils::isTrue;
075      Predicate<Long> nm1 = ObjectUtils::isNotMinusOne;
076      return om
077         .appendFirst(ne, "collectionFormat", a.collectionFormat(), a.cf())
078         .appendIf(ne, "default", joinnl(a._default(), a.df()))
079         .appendFirst(nec, "enum", parseSet(a._enum()), parseSet(a.e()))
080         .appendIf(nf, "exclusiveMaximum", a.exclusiveMaximum() || a.emax())
081         .appendIf(nf, "exclusiveMinimum", a.exclusiveMinimum() || a.emin())
082         .appendFirst(ne, "format", a.format(), a.f())
083         .appendIf(nem, "items", parseMap(a.items()))
084         .appendFirst(ne, "maximum", a.maximum(), a.max())
085         .appendFirst(nm1, "maxItems", a.maxItems(), a.maxi())
086         .appendFirst(nm1, "maxLength", a.maxLength(), a.maxl())
087         .appendFirst(ne, "minimum", a.minimum(), a.min())
088         .appendFirst(nm1, "minItems", a.minItems(), a.mini())
089         .appendFirst(nm1, "minLength", a.minLength(), a.minl())
090         .appendFirst(ne, "multipleOf", a.multipleOf(), a.mo())
091         .appendFirst(ne, "pattern", a.pattern(), a.p())
092         .appendFirst(ne, "type", a.type(), a.t())
093         .appendIf(nf, "uniqueItems", a.uniqueItems() || a.ui())
094         .appendIf(ne, "$ref", a.$ref())
095      ;
096   }

514   private static class Impl extends AnnotationImpl implements SubItems {
515
516      private final boolean emax, emin, exclusiveMaximum, exclusiveMinimum, ui, uniqueItems;
517      private final long maxi, maxItems, maxl, maxLength, mini, minItems, minl, minLength;
518      private final String $ref, cf, collectionFormat, f, format, max, maximum, min, minimum, mo, multipleOf, p, pattern, t, type;
519      private final String[] _default, _enum, df, e, items;
520
521      Impl(Builder b) {
522         super(b);
523         this.$ref = b.$ref;
524         this._default = copyOf(b._default);
525         this._enum = copyOf(b._enum);
526         this.cf = b.cf;
527         this.collectionFormat = b.collectionFormat;
528         this.df = copyOf(b.df);
529         this.e = copyOf(b.e);
530         this.emax = b.emax;
531         this.emin = b.emin;
532         this.exclusiveMaximum = b.exclusiveMaximum;
533         this.exclusiveMinimum = b.exclusiveMinimum;
534         this.f = b.f;
535         this.format = b.format;
536         this.items = copyOf(b.items);
537         this.max = b.max;
538         this.maxi = b.maxi;
539         this.maximum = b.maximum;
540         this.maxItems = b.maxItems;
541         this.maxl = b.maxl;
542         this.maxLength = b.maxLength;
543         this.min = b.min;
544         this.mini = b.mini;
545         this.minimum = b.minimum;
546         this.minItems = b.minItems;
547         this.minl = b.minl;
548         this.minLength = b.minLength;
549         this.mo = b.mo;
550         this.multipleOf = b.multipleOf;
551         this.p = b.p;
552         this.pattern = b.pattern;
553         this.t = b.t;
554         this.type = b.type;
555         this.ui = b.ui;
556         this.uniqueItems = b.uniqueItems;
557         postConstruct();
558      }
